imdb.plot outline: Okaerinasaimase, goshujinsama. The Maids at Arcane Maid Cafe are all competing against one another to become the one and only 2017 Oshimaid. But underground trading, theft, and embezzlement of trading pins are happening while the honest maids are trying to collect them legitimately. So who will win in this ultra-low budget contest to earn enough pins to become the next Oshimaid. Find out on The Maid Cafe.
